content:
Get-AzureRmAppServicePlanMetrics

In this Article

Syntax

Get-AzureRmAppServicePlanMetrics [-ResourceGroupName] <String> [-Name] <String> [-Metrics] <String[]>
 [-StartTime] <DateTime> [[-EndTime] <DateTime>] [-Granularity] <String> [-InstanceDetails]
 [<CommonParameters>]
Get-AzureRmAppServicePlanMetrics [-AppServicePlan] <ServerFarmWithRichSku> [-Metrics] <String[]>
 [-StartTime] <DateTime> [[-EndTime] <DateTime>] [-Granularity] <String> [-InstanceDetails]
 [<CommonParameters>]

Description

The Get-AzureRmAppServicePlanMetrics gets App Service Plan metrics.

Examples

1:

PS C:\>Get-AzureRmAppServicePlanMetrics -ResourceGroupName "Default-Web-WestUS" -Name "ContosoAppServPlan" -StartTime 2016-11-30T22:00:00Z -EndTime 2016-11-30T22:30:00Z -Granularity PT1M -Metrics ["CPU Percentage"]

This command gets CPU percentage of the App Service Plan per minute(PT1M - Poll Time 1 minute) between StartTime and EndTime
